<HEADLINE> Rockets Returns Title at Chinese Basketball </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NINGBO, Zhejiang province, April 25 (Xinhua) -- Defending
champions Bayi Rockets swept Liaoning Hunters 3-0 after scoring a
110--96 victory in the third game of the best-of-five finals at
the 1998-99 season of the Chinese First Division Basketball League
here on Sunday.
</P>
<P>
It was the fourth consecutive title for the Bayi Rockets, who
led the first half by 59-51.
</P>
<P>
Liaoning Hunters has also been the runners-up to the Rockets in
all the first four seasons of the 12-team Chinese League which
started in the year of 1995. 
</P>
